OL,3,CSister's fight for Infected Blood
OL,4,Cmemorial garden at Chelsea Flower Show
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV reporter Rachel Hepworth
OL,7,Fwent to meet Amanda at her studio in
OL,8,FWest Sussex.
OL,10,FThe sister of a Surrey man who died as
OL,11,Fa result of the infected blood scandal
OL,12,F- is fundraising to create a memorial
OL,13,Fgarden honouring him and other victims.
OL,15,FA popular radio presenter in
OL,16,FGuildford, Simon Cummings was a
OL,17,Fhaemophiliac who died in 1996, after
OL,18,Fcontracting HIV from contaminated
OL,19,Fblood.
