OL,3,CSister's fight for Infected Blood
OL,4,Cmemorial garden at Chelsea Flower Show
OL,6,FHis sister, garden designer Amanda
OL,7,FPatton from West Sussex, wants to
OL,8,Fcreate a fitting memorial at next
OL,9,Fyear's Chelsea Flower show, but is
OL,10,Frunning out of time to raise the money.
OL,12,FSimon was a well-known name and a big
OL,13,Fpersonality on Surrey Sound during the
OL,14,F1980s and 90s, even organising a
OL,15,Fcharity single featuring Sir Cliff
OL,16,FRichard.
OL,18,FSo his death, aged just 38, from HIV,
OL,19,Fleft a huge void.
