OL,3,CSister's fight for Infected Blood
OL,4,Cmemorial garden at Chelsea Flower Show
OL,6,F"At the time, nobody knew why he
OL,7,Fdied," says Amanda. "They just knew
OL,8,Fthat suddenly he was off air because
OL,9,Fthere was a huge amount of stigma
OL,10,Fsurrounding HIV in the early eighties."
OL,12,FShe was among hundreds of people who
OL,13,Fgave evidence at the Infected Blood
OL,14,FInquiry, which in May concluded
OL,15,Fcatastrophic and systemic failings led
OL,16,Fto thousands of avoidable deaths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
