OL,3,CSister's fight for Infected Blood
OL,4,Cmemorial garden at Chelsea Flower Show
OL,6,F"It will be called 'Simon's Garden'
OL,7,Fbecause it personalises the tragedy,
OL,8,Fand help people to focus on individual
OL,9,Fstories.
OL,11,F"This isn't just a victim number. It's
OL,12,Fa person who was taken from as far too
OL,13,Fyoung. These are all unwitting
OL,14,Ffamilies that this has happened to."
OL,16,FAmanda hopes the garden will be a
OL,17,Fplace of solace, but also ensure the
OL,18,Ftragedy and her brother, are never
OL,19,Fforgotten.
